hat kind of people there can I ujar WOrk again in a few days.\nbe in this world, but when I think of the guidance you give me, I\u2019ve got to I Sister Nellie Connors, financial secretary of Local Union No. 20, Steu\nsubtract 9S%.\u201d\n\u201cYou don\u2019t do me justice, Luther,\u201d his father said. I Jack Davis and Fred Davison, Minerva potters, were among those who\n\u201cMaybe not,\u201d Little Luther admitted. \u201cBut neither could a truck driver, I attended the Kohler-Goodman boxing show at Canton last Friday evening,\na mule skinner, a fishwife, a hack driver, or a soldier compelled to drive a I and both declare it was a \u201cpeach.\u201d\nlieutenant to an officers\u2019 ball.\u201d I Elizah Hutton of Mannington, W. Va., was an East Palestine visitor last\n\u201cI don\u2019t know what you mean,\u201d said Mr. Dilworth. |week.\n\u201cIt\u2019s probably just as well,\u201d Little Luther sand. \u201cBut let\u2019s get on to other I Brother John Charlton of East Palestine has complained to his shopmates\npoints. How much am I going to get for food, lodging and clothes?\u201d |that some clerical looking chap living in close proximity to his aristocratic\n\u201cWell,\u201d his father said, \u201cI was thinking of giving you $1.50 a week.\u201d I hen coop, deliberately invaded his hennery apartments sometime between\n\u201c$1.50 a week!\u201d Luther exclaimed. \u201cWhy, it will cost me 20 times that|sunrise and sunset a few nights ago, and swiped, kidnaped and carried off\nmuch. Do you know the price of I his big black rooster. The owner authorizes a reward of $5 for the return of\n\u201cPrice doesn\u2019t enter into it,\u201d said Mr. Dilworth sternly. \u201cAre you trying |^s no questions asked. TT n\nto take management\u2019s prerogatives away\u2014I mean are you trying to take| For some reason unknown to Local Union No. the Colonial Pottery\nparents\u2019 prerogatives away from parents?\u201d I company, has returned to the eight-hole sagger. It will be r